        <div><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> From <a href="http://www.planeteverquest.com/">PlanetEverQuest</a>:<br><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> <blockquote>This week's <a href="http://www.planeteverquest.com/features/quiz/index.shtml">EQ Quiz is about Enchanters</a>. Their spells focus on manipulation of the mind, and this mental acuteness gives them more spells than any other class.<br><br>With spells like Clarity and Charm it's no wonder that Enchanters are sought after by groups all over Norrath. But regenerating mana and charming creatures isn't all that they excell at .. take the test and see how much you know about these mystic snake charmers... <br><br>This "just for fun" quiz will challenge all that you know, or might not know, about the charming mystics of the realms.  Clarity and haste aren't the only things that enchanters can cast.  Take the test and see how much you know .. or don't know about the Enchanters of EverQuest.<br><br><a href="http://www.planeteverquest.com/">PlanetEverQuest</a><br></blockquote>Thanks! </font> </font>
